sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as AI Studio
  participant Agent as Agent Orchestrator
  participant Tutor as AI Tutor
  participant DB as agents schema

  UI->>Agent: POST /agents/run
  Agent->>Tutor: RAG ask lab concept
  Tutor-->>Agent: Answer + citations
  Agent->>Tutor: Food for thought prompts
  Tutor-->>Agent: Reflection questions
  Agent->>DB: Save run + steps
  Agent-->>UI: Multi-step coaching response
